    "Rakhi is a thread that binds two souls in a bond of joy forever...  It connects the happy memories of yesterday with the happiness to come tomorow.  Today I'm remembering with joy the special days we shared and wishing you happiness & Good Luck not just today but always...  Happy Raksha Bandhan  ",
    "No matter how far I am... You r with me in my thoughts... And memories of the fun times we have shared the laughter & smiles... are in my heart.   Wishing you happiness and smiles today on Raksha Bandhan & always.  ",
