    "Know why RAKHI is called Khushiyon Ka Bandhan?  Bcoz its all about...  R - Reafferming love & affection. A - A prayer for long life & success. K - Keeping memories alive. H - Happiness & Laughter I - Innurable shared stories.   Thinking of you today & wishing you all the joy in the world.  ",
